{"tid":602092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有心事嘅入黎擺低 無心事嘅入黎吹水(52.5)","createTime":"2018-03-22T18:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T18:11:18.000Z","uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffec5700674588adba041f0d0c1c91f498610306","tid":602092,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"熄登避難區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續有心事入嚟擺低 無心事入嚟吹水<br />\n絕非小圈子 有心事就算見到吹緊水都唔使怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲比既意見會比較直擊 大家唔好嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲巴絲講野好低b 因為都係無聊野傾到冇野傾先講低b嘢<br />\n所以好歡迎新話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲會po啲好黑既嘢<br />\n又有時候會無啦啦變左成人台<br />\n如果你handle唔到可以唔理佢地<br />\nhandle唔到都無辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人討論歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82bde88ec95d21615856506904a1d905fd7a7c4","tid":602092,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n啊！！！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">啊！！！！！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啊！！！！！！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啊！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/ytimg.googleusercontent.com/vi/9PmLQXLSBoY/mqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fytimg.googleusercontent.com%2Fvi%2F9PmLQXLSBoY%2Fmqdefault.jpg&h=c5e15af5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a021dca8ccd354e732d8b53fcee4809176d0d67b","tid":602092,"uid"